```python
def insert_before_character(string):
    return string.replace('o', 'oo')

# Example Usage
print(insert_before_character("Hello"))  # "Hello"
print(insert_before_character("world"))  # "woorld"
print(insert_before_character("Good"))  # "Good"
print(insert_before_character("morning"))  # "moorning"
```
